Events

static NotificationEventHandler OnNotification
 Sent when an OpenFeint notification should appear on screen. This is sent regardless of whether or not notifications are allowed. If notifications are not allowed, use this event to determine when you should display your own message.
static DeferredResultEventHandler OnHighScoreSubmitted
 Sent upon success or failure of a high score submission.
static DeferredResultEventHandler OnAchievementUpdated
 Sent upon success or failure of an achievement progression update. If the achievement has already been unlocked locally, this event will not be sent.
static DeferredResultEventHandler OnAchievementUnlocked
 Sent upon success or failure of an achievement unlock. If the achievement has already been unlocked locally, this event will not be sent.
static StartedChallengeEventHandler OnStartedChallenge
 Sent when the user starts a challenge. You will need to subsequently call one of the GetChallengeData method to get the challenge data that was sent with the challenge.
static GeneralEventHandler OnRestartedChallenge
 Sent when the user restarts a challenge.
static GeneralEventHandler OnRestartedCreateChallenge
 Sent when the user restarts a challenge that he is trying to create. This message is only sent if stronger attempts are enabled for challenges and if the challenge was a multi-attempt challenge.
static GeneralEventHandler OnCompletedChallengeScreenClosed
 Sent when the completed challenge screen is closed.
static GeneralEventHandler OnSendChallengeScreenClosed
 Sent when the send challenge screen is closed.
static GeneralEventHandler OnUserSentChallenges
 Sent when the user sends a challenge to another user.
static DeferredResultEventHandler OnChallengeResultSubmitted
 Sent upon success or failure of a challenge result submission.
static DeferredResultEventHandler OnUploadedCloudBlob
 Send upon success or failure of uploading a blob to the cloud.
static UserLogInEventHandler OnUserLoggedInToOF
 Sent when a user successfully connects to the OpenFeint servers.
static UserLogInEventHandler OnUserLoggedOutOfOF
 Sent when a user explicitly logs out from OpenFeint (though does not get sent when user switches accounts; only OnUserLoggedInToOF gets sent in that instance).
static IconLoadEventHandler OnAchievementIconLoad
 Sent when an Icon successfully is written to local storage or sent when an Icon retrieval fails.
